      • getAll

        public java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,int[]> getAll()
        Function returns all of the scribbler sensors (not fluke) in a hashmap. Each associated array for a key is of variable length, depending on the type of sensor. IR array has size 2; LIGHT array has size 3; LINE array has size 2; STALL array has size 1;
        Returns:
        hashmap with keys: "IR", "LINE", "LIGHT", and "STALL"
